    "      \"Epoch: 01, Loss: 0.6986, Train Acc: 0.5287, Test Acc: 0.5714\\n\",\n",
    "      \"Epoch: 05, Loss: 0.6905, Train Acc: 0.5287, Test Acc: 0.5714\\n\",\n",
